Ruoth Nyasaye oluongo Bezalel gi Oholiab

(Wuok 
35  .
30  —
36  .
1  )


1  Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho ni Musa niya, 
2  “Ng’eni aseyiero Bezalel wuod Hur, ja Juda. 
3  Asepong’e gi Roho mara mondo obed gi lony kod nyalo, kaachiel gi rieko mar ng’eyo tije duto mag lwedo, kaka: 
4  goro kido mabeyo mag dhahabu gi fedha kod mula, 
5  kendo ng’ado kite michomo, kaachiel gi payo bao, kata tich moro amora mar lwedo. 
6  To bende aseyiero Oholiab wuod Ahisamak, ja Dan, mondo okonye, kendo asemiyo jotich duto molony rieko mondo olos gigo duto masechiki. 
7  Ginilos Hemb Romo, kod Sandug Rapar gi raumne kod gik moko duto mag hema, 
8  kaka mesa gi gige, kod rachung taya mag dhahabu maler gi gige, 
9  kod kendo-mar-misango miwang’oe ubani, gi mar misango miwang’o pep, gi gige, kod karaya mar lwok gi rachungine, 
10  kod lep dolo malich mag Harun jadolo gi mag yawuote, ma girwako ka gitiyo tich dolo, 
11  kod mor wir gi ubani mang’ue ng’ar mar Kama Ler. Ka giloso gigo duto, to nyaka giti mana kaka asenyisi.”

Oket chieng’ Sabato mondo obed ranyisi


12  Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho ni Musa niya, 
13  “Nyis jo-Israel kama, ‘Nyaka urit chieng’ Sabatona, nikech chieng’ yueyono en ranyisi manie kinda kodu kaachiel gi nyikwau nyaka chieng’, mondo ung’e ni an e Ruoth Nyasaye mopuodhou. 
14  Kuom mano nyaka urit Sabato nikech en chieng’ moket mondo obednu maler. Ka ng’ato ok orite, to nyaka nege. Ng’ato ang’ata motiyo chieng’no nyaka ng’ad kare oko kuom jowetene. 
15  

Unyalo tiyo tijeu kuom ndalo auchiel, to chieng’ mar abiriyo en chieng’ yueyo maler, mowal ni Ruoth Nyasaye. Ng’ato ang’ata manoti chieng’ Sabato nyaka negi. 
16  Jo-Israel nyaka rit chieng’ Sabato kuom tiengegi duto kaka chieng’ ma gisesingore rito nyaka chieng. 
17  

En ranyisi mochwere manie kinda kod jo-Israel, nimar an Ruoth Nyasaye, nachueyo polo gi piny kuom ndalo auchiel, to chieng’ mar abiriyo naweyo tich, mayueyo.’ ”


18  Kane Ruoth Nyasaye osetieko wuoyo gi Musa e got Sinai, nomiye kite mopamore ariyo mag rapar. Gin e kite ariyo mane Nyasaye ondikoe gi lith lwete.

